## SEGMENT 3 — Setting Claude Up to Know Your Business (12 minutes)

**The point you're making:** There are two tools in Claude that make it act like it already knows your business — the System Prompt (in Projects) and the memory/context file you paste in at the start of a session. Walk them through both. Make it tactical.

